Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rainbase"                 "Alubarna"\N      "Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"\N"Spiders Café"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed\Nsince a single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people take up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fanning the flames\Nof rebellion is Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To stop his scheme,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and company stormed\Nthe enemy hideout in Rainbase,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they wound up captured instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the operation Crocodile speaks of?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Vivi's wish be swallowed\Nup by the burning land?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just turned noon.\NThe operation is beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Operation Utopia Commences!\NThe Swell of Rebellion Stirs"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold suspicion, Koza.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know His Majesty's\Ncharacter very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you old people say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't follow you here to\NYuba for the king's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebel army is over\N100,000 strong now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there've been casualties, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little rain will clear him\Nof these strange suspicions. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The canal's been destroyed!\N--Who would do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can't bring water to this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't rained for over a year now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erumalu is done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold suspicion, Koza...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to suspect you,\Nbut people are dying of thirst!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not be using it,\Nbut you do have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Wait for natural rain.\NDance Powder summons misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit should be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebellion might even stop\Nif there's at least some rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would only result in a greater calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not as easy to use as you think, Koza.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to watch\Ntowns dry up anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit\Nsince the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have changed. I can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to come here to take your rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this country headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does the answer lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have bad news, Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:04:59.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alubarna Palace"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Terrible news,\NChaka-sama! It's His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd!\NHave you searched everywhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Not only the palace, but the\Ngarden and storehouses as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he have left\Nin the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the question!\NThe king's security was top-notch,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he couldn't have escaped our eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the king hide himself\Njust before going to battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search! Outside the palace and the towns!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pell excels in finding people,\Nbut as luck would have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's busy conducting\Nreconnaissance in Rainbase...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has happened to His Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to act recklessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you planning\Nto do to Alabasta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to know the type of\Npeople I look down on most of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hypocrites who treasure the\Nso-called "happiness of the people."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to kill my father?!\NAs if you could ever do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to shout.\NI have no such intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not even worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to let Cobra taste\Nhumiliation far crueler than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crueler than death?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no way for a princess\Nof a kingdom to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask one more time!\NJust what is Operation Utopia?! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Do you realize where\Nyou stand in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a valiant princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But very well.\NThe operation has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you about my plan\Nto end this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Operation Utopia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible news,\NChaka-sama! It's His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! Did you find him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! He's apparently in Nanohana!\NThe information is certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But, unbelievably enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Koza!\N--Koza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--We're coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why suddenly now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he fallen as far as he can?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold suspicion, Koza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:08:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he do something\Nthis nonsensical?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:01.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nanohana"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you heard.\NI am honestly apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was I, Cobra, the king of Alabasta,\Nwho stole this country's rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra-sama...\NHow can you joke like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used Dance Powder to keep the rain\Nin the capital city of Alubarna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As li'l ol' king-- no, I mean, as a\Nrespected king, I cannot go thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That may be so,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but many have died due to lack\Nof food and water as a result!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you allow--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am aware of that, of course.\NAnd that many oases have dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But some sacrifices are unavoidable\Nif we are to protect the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew how miserable things were,\Nyet you only helped yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's far too selfish even for you, King!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is a mere cretin like you trying\Nto talk back to me, the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to Nanohana to\Napologize for what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother died in Yuba, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come all the way to\Nthis city for one other reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, Dance Powder is\Noutlawed by the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If word of its use is leaked outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Headquarters will take\Naction and destroy said country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you may remember that\Nlarge amounts of Dance Powder
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were found being smuggled\Ninto this town two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is necessary to eliminate all\Ntraces of that incident. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:10:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! If we are to be rid\Nof that terrible incident forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must be rid of this city and all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--W-What?!\N--That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to die just 'cause you ordered it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you steal the rain that\Nall the towns are drying up, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna avenge everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Burn Nanohana to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Koza!\N--Koza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--King!\N--Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to apologize, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you're saying?!\NThis is an incredible insult!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who's been\Nusing Dance Powder to--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why are you so angry?\N--Koza...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Surely even you can appreciate...\N--Sire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...that I...\N--You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how the people felt\Nas they died in the dried-up towns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't have hatred or anger for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It isn't the king's fault!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He's a great person!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as they died, they all\Nsaid that, with faith in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what happens to them now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you at least lie\Nand say you're innocent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Koza-san!\N--Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we fight because\Nthe kingdom-- no, everyone--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to know that answer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that's why I fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant ship is about to crash! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:14:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's toppling over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a final operation,\Nthat sure lacked exertion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we ever had any\Nexerting work before this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! Now light the\Nfires and let's retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't feel relaxed without this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza! Say something! Koza! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The royal army disappeared!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How deux you like my kingliness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Mr. 2, Bon Clay-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The damn royal army lit fires and ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry!\N--Put out the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to meet up with Mr. 2 outside town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alubarna's the finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vague! My favorite word is "vague"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now whether or not the king\Nwill stay king is vague!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Bunchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's west of town, Mr. 2, Bon Clay-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The king turned\Ninto a weird ballerina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! It won't go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Everyone's being tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a naughty little boy.\NWhat do you think he's discovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn imbecile\Nmade a careless slip-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it there's no use in\Nasking you to stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water! We need more water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That's for my shop!\NCan you pay for it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now, you idiot! The town is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Put out the fires!\N--Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! We can't\Nkeep up with the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should probably run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Koza!\NYou're not the type to die like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Take Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! Not even children are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! I'll stop\Nthe bleeding! Don't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think!\NEveryone's being tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... end this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact all of our branches!\NThis will be our final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, but we don't\Nhave nearly enough weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know that ship that just crashed?\NIt was an armory ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Seriously?!\N--Yeah! It was full of weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like divine guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? A little pipsqueak\Nsaw me? So sorry! So, so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. Now Mr. 4's team\Njust needs to do its thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fatty and Old Hag know\Nhow to get things done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapping the king\Nwill be nothing to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me, rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Alabasta of old is long dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final battle!\NWe're going to capture Alubarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to launch an all-out assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king must pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll build a new country!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:54.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Meanwhile, at Alubarna Palace"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:18:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra-sama would never do\Nsuch a thing! It must be a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the time between his disappearance\Nand his arrival fit perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuses no longer hold any water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,News of the Nanohana incident\Nhave spread throughout Alabasta,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rebel soldiers\Neverywhere have responded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, the citizens\Nwho had faith in His Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have begun taking up weapons\Nout of hatred for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their numbers are unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire country is infuriated\Nand heading for Alubarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no stopping things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, make your decision!\NWe will obey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the king's words from\Nyesterday are blurred now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In what do I put my trust?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! We need only\Nfulfill our given duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the royal guards\Nof the Alabasta Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:19:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kingdom should crumble\Nin the absence of its king!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the truth you see before you!\NProtect this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter the rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:19.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rainbase"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrifying plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation you once\Nparticipated in has now blossomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you listen closely, you could\Nprobably hear the howls of Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they all think the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Protect Alabasta."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Protect Alabasta. Protect Alabasta."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so cruel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it just heartrending?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:20:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love for the kingdom will be\Nwhat destroys the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he stupid? Did he not hear what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely stupid.\NBut that's also why he's our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile! I will kick your ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many moves I've made\Nto make it this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sabotage to instigate the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Directing the royal army's misconduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you any idea why I'd go to\Nsuch lengths to attain this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd understand anything\Ninside your rotten head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a bad-mouthed princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. What are you\Ntrying to do, Miss Wednesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop you! There's still time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just get to Alubarna east of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get there before the rebel army,\NI may be able to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely refuse to let you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to talk about it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:22:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even say half of it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm by your side, I glitter\Nevery time we share a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smile you gently gave me\Nwas a very happy and kind one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glory glory you're my shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're here, even\Nthese tears turn to courage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be strong,\NI want to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll make it there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:22:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that insanely huge alligator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! There's an alligator\Ngrowing from that banana!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.99,0:23:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The alligator swallowed the key to our cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What a troublesome gator!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that eyebrow freak\Ndoing at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there a little longer,\Neveryone! I will bring back help!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Terrifying Bananagators and Mr. Prince"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
